Name: Monkey vs Dino
About the game: Choose for whom you will fight a dinosaur and a monkey, fight. You can choose one of two characters, a monkey, or a dinosaur. If you choose a dinosaur, you will need to defeat the monkey. And if you choose a monkey, you will have to defeat the dinosaur. Control the character with the keyboard and mouse, use different combinations of blows.
